OL,3,CArchbishop of York 'deeply sorry', as
OL,4,Che faces calls to resign
OL,6,FPressure mounts on the Archbishop of
OL,7,FYork to resign over the handling of a
OL,8,Fsex abuse case within the Church, ITV
OL,9,FNews' Rachel Townsend explains
OL,11,FThe Archbishop of York has said he is
OL,12,F"deeply sorry" he was not able to take
OL,13,Faction earlier when dealing with sex
OL,14,Foffender David Tudor while he was
OL,15,FBishop of Chelmsford.
OL,17,FStephen Cottrell, the Church's second-
OL,18,Fmost-senior bishop, is facing calls to
OL,19,Fresign over his handling of a sex
OL,20,Fabuse case within the church.
