OL,3,CArchbishop of York 'deeply sorry', as
OL,4,Che faces calls to resign
OL,6,FIt comes just weeks before he was due
OL,7,Fto take charge of the Church of
OL,8,FEngland as interim leader, after
OL,9,FJustin Welby, the current Archbishop
OL,10,Fof Canterbury, quit over failures in
OL,11,Fthe handling of a separate abuse case.
OL,13,FA BBC investigation reported that Mr
OL,14,FCottrell allegedly let priest David
OL,15,FTudor stay in post in the diocese,
OL,16,Fdespite knowing he had been barred
OL,17,Ffrom being alone with children, and
OL,18,Fhad paid compensation to a sexual
OL,19,Fabuse victim.
