OL,3,CArchbishop of York 'deeply sorry', as
OL,4,Che faces calls to resign
OL,6,FResponding to the report in a personal
OL,7,Fstatement, Mr Cottrell said he was
OL,8,F"deeply sorry we were not able to take
OL,9,Faction earlier".
OL,11,FHe said he faced a "horrible and
OL,12,Fintolerable" situation when he became
OL,13,FBishop of Chelmsford in 2010, and was
OL,14,Foriginally briefed on the situation
OL,15,Fregarding David Tudor.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
