OL,3,CArchbishop of York 'deeply sorry', as
OL,4,Che faces calls to resign
OL,6,FHe said: "This morning's news coverage
OL,7,Fincorrectly implies that no action was
OL,8,Ftaken until 2024. That is not the
OL,9,Fcase. In my capacity as Bishop of
OL,10,FChelmsford, I suspended David Tudor
OL,11,Ffrom office at the first opportunity,
OL,12,Fwhen a new victim came forward to the
OL,13,Fpolice in 2019. Up until 2019, there
OL,14,Fwere no legal grounds to take
OL,15,Falternative action."
OL,17,FHe said it was "not possible to remove
OL,18,FDavid Tudor from office" until "fresh
OL,19,Fcomplaints were made" in 2019, "when a
OL,20,Fvictim bravely spoke to the police".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
