OL,3,CArchbishop of York 'deeply sorry', as
OL,4,Che faces calls to resign
OL,6,FMr Cottrell said once this happened,
OL,7,Fhe "acted immediately."
OL,9,F"I suspended David Tudor from all
OL,10,Fministry pending the investigation and
OL,11,Fsubsequent tribunal hearing in which
OL,12,Fhe was removed from office and
OL,13,Fprohibited from ministry for life," he
OL,14,Fsaid.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/13
