OL,3,CArchbishop of York 'deeply sorry', as
OL,4,Che faces calls to resign
OL,6,FIt was only in October of this year
OL,7,Fthat Tudor was banned from ministry
OL,8,Ffor life, after admitting what the
OL,9,FChurch described as serious sexual
OL,10,Fabuse including two girls aged 15 and
OL,11,F16, when he was a priest in the
OL,12,FDiocese of Southwark.
OL,14,FMr Cottrell said: "I want victims and
OL,15,Fsurvivors to know that everything was
OL,16,Fdone to understand, assess and manage
OL,17,Fthe risk. I also want them to know
OL,18,Fthat I fully welcome the outcome of
OL,19,Fthe Tribunal in October 2024."
