OL,4,Che faces calls to resign
OL,6,FThe Church of England said the BBC
OL,7,Finvestigation had showed a "catalogue
OL,8,Fof past safeguarding decisions that
OL,9,Fallowed someone who was considered a
OL,10,Frisk in the 1980s to return to
OL,11,Fministry in the 1990s."
OL,13,F"This should never have happened," it
OL,14,Fadded.
OL,16,FA woman who was paid compensation by
OL,17,FTudor over claims he sexually abused
OL,18,Fher as a child told the BBC that Mr
OL,19,FCottrell's failure to act when he was
OL,20,Ftold about the payment means he should
OL,21,F"leave the Church".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
