OL,6,FBishop of Newcastle Helen-Ann Hartley
OL,7,Ftold ITV News it was "lamentable" more
OL,8,Fwasn't done by Mr Cottrell at the time.
OL,10,F"I think it's lamentable that he
OL,11,Fdidn't push on the lines that I've
OL,12,Foutlined, so I think that because of
OL,13,Fthat he lacks credibility to lead on
OL,14,Fsafeguarding at what is an
OL,15,Funprecedented and crucial time in the
OL,16,Flife of the Church of England."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/13
