OL,3,CArchbishop of York 'deeply sorry', as
OL,4,Che faces calls to resign
OL,6,FWhen asked whether Stephen Cottrell
OL,7,Fshould lead the Church of England, she
OL,8,Fsaid he "has significant questions
OL,9,Fhanging over him about how he did not
OL,10,Fdeal, in my opinion, adequately with a
OL,11,Fsafeguarding issue."
OL,13,F"I think it completely undermines his
OL,14,Fcredibility to say that he finds
OL,15,Fsafeguarding something that's urgent
OL,16,Fand important that we need to get
OL,17,Fright," she said, "I don't see how you
OL,18,Fcan speak publicly on that and yet
OL,19,Fhave been shown to have not acted in a
OL,20,Fway where that would have been
OL,21,Fpossible."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/13
