OL,3,CArchbishop of York 'deeply sorry', as
OL,4,Che faces calls to resign
OL,6,FIn his statement on Monday, Mr
OL,7,FCottrell pledged that he would "do
OL,8,Fwhat I can" to bring about independent
OL,9,Fscrutiny and safeguarding in the
OL,10,FChurch.
OL,12,FHe said processes within the Church
OL,13,Fhad changed, and that the Tudor case
OL,14,Fwould be handled differently now.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/13
