OL,3,CArchbishop of York 'deeply sorry', as
OL,4,Che faces calls to resign
OL,6,F"The Church of England now needs
OL,7,Findependent scrutiny of safeguarding
OL,8,Fso that those who do have
OL,9,Funderstandable frustrations and
OL,10,Fconcerns can have their voices heard
OL,11,Fand those of us who have
OL,12,Fresponsibility for managing these
OL,13,Fsituations can be helped to avoid them
OL,14,Fand resolve them," Mr Cottrell said.
OL,16,F"I have publicly supported this for
OL,17,Fmany years. I pledge myself to do what
OL,18,FI can to achieve it."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/13
