OL,6,FMr Cottrell is due to take over
OL,7,Ftemporarily as the Archbishop of
OL,8,FCanterbury from January 6, when Justin
OL,9,FWelby is due to quit.
OL,11,FMr Welby announced last month that he
OL,12,Fwould resign, after initially
OL,13,Fdeclining to do so, following the
OL,14,FMakin Review into the handling of
OL,15,Fallegations against serial abuser John
OL,16,FSmyth.
